    "date": "2022-03-31T19:23:44Z",
    "text": "Guardianship Accountability Act of 2021 This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services (HHS) to create a National Resource Center on Guardianship for the publication of resources and data relating to court-determined adult guardianships. Further, HHS must award at least 5%\u00a0of certain grant funds for state programs related to overseeing the administration of court-appointed guardian arrangements."
